    "content" : [ {
      "type" : "text",
      "text" : "From Europe are flights with Air France through LAX, Los Angeles or with Qatar Airways that has a codeshare agreement with Air New Zealand through Auckland the two most accessible options. If you are stopping by New Zealand on your way to French Polynesia, be sure to check out this post about the best campsites in New Zealand."
