    "content" : [ {
      "type" : "text",
      "text" : "French Polynesia is made up of five archipelagos, all more different, than the other. There are only about 280,000 lucky islanders living on 67 inhabited islands and atolls. With over 70% of the population concentrated on the big island of Tahiti."
    } ]
