      "textAlign" : "left"
    },
    "content" : [ {
      "type" : "text",
      "text" : "It's important to know that while there are local flights between the islands inside each Archipelago. So will you have to transit through Tahiti when traveling from one archipelago to another.  Be aware that you often will, you have to stay a night in Tahiti before taking your onward flight to the next Archipelago early the next morning. Flights to smaller islands and atolls are often booked out months in advance."
